title: DDFP 412: Week 14 review & Losing your job to an injury
itunes:title: DDFP 412: Week 14 review & Losing your job to an injury
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank, Maurice Jones-Drew, and Ike Taylor to review week 14, including Andy Dalton's injury. The guys also talk about how a potential loss for the Carolina Panthers may beneficial. Lastly, Ike takes questions for yet another installment of "Dear Ikey".
